Manage your open source information⎯whether for individual productivity, team collaboration, or company-wide operations.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(10px) translateY(5px) translateZ(0)"><img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r7m53vrk/production/02e19effe217f9efe2803c86e9be1d780d4c559b-1280x720.gif"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="w-full flex px-1 largeTablet:px-6 mb-10"><div class="relative flex-1 bg-gradient-to-b border-b-0 border-l-0 border-r-[#F87216] border-t-[#F87216] border h-[200px] w-full to-gray-800"><img class="absolute -right-[28px] -top-[28px]" src="/icons/quote.svg" alt="Ending line" style="opacity:0;transform:scale(0.2) translateZ(0)"/></div><div class="flex-1"></div></div></div><div style="padding-bottom:105px;padding-top:0px" class="w-full max-w-[1256px] mx-auto px-6 h-fit flex justify-center flex-col items-center"><h2 style="text-align:center" class="w-full font-bold text-textPrimary tracking-[-0.02em] text-3xl
